#  ConsolePacketSniffer

A C# console app that captures and analyzes Xbox/PlayStation/game network packets and shows where each IP is from using IP geolocation.

##  Features

- Live packet sniffing using SharpPcap
- IP geolocation (country, city, ISP)
- Flags for Xbox Live, PlayStation Network, and Game traffic
- UDP port analysis
- Console output only (no GUI)

##  Requirements

- Windows OS
- [.NET 6.0 SDK](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download)
- [Npcap](https://npcap.com/) (Install in **WinPcap-compatible mode**)
- Run as Administrator

##  How to Run

1. Clone this repo
2. Open terminal and run:

```bash
dotnet restore
dotnet run
